info
C++ Coding Booster is a program to enhance c++ coding skill and typing skill with 3 minigame.
Hopefully, user will acquire more coding skill and entertainment we offer.


mode 1 typing master
Blocks contain c++ code falling rapidly from the top.
User will need to type the code in those blocks.
The game is over if the blockspile reach the top. 


mode 2 quiz warrior
There will be 2 types of quiz.
Multiple choice - choose the correct items for it's question.
Ouput - type output from the question.
User must answer correctly to proceed to next question or use skip option.


mode 3 program builder
User will have to write c++ program from each stage.
Complete the stage to unlocks more stages.




